message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are: cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CY. The paper deals with the problem of generating natural language questions from keyword-based web queries, which involves natural language processing, machine translation, and information retrieval. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
